          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This isn’t particularly surprising. Democratic politicians, liberal pundits, and corporate media outlets have mastered the art of solely blaming Trump for problems that the past Democratic administration contributed to and the current Democratic administration has refused to fix. That train never derails. It is always on time.",
            "type": "text",
