      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The problem, though, is that this anti-Trump narrative — while rooted in the facts of Trump’s decision to repeal the brake rule — has been extrapolated and distorted to the point of becoming a lie. And not just any old lie, but the most calculated kind of lie: a lie by deliberate omission.",
