      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That truth is clear: While Trump’s decision to repeal the brake was deplorable, Obama administration regulators had previously decided to ignore federal safety officials and side with chemical industry lobbyists to narrow the definition of “high-hazard flammable train.” That decision exempted trains like Norfolk Southern’s from ",
