        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "If you peruse the glut of national media coverage about the derailment, you will find almost no reference to this part of the story, even though it is the foundational deregulatory event — one just as pivotal as Trump’s subsequent decision to repeal the brake rule.",
            "type": "text",
