      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It allows credulous liberals to continue ensconcing themselves in a warm womb of ignorance, telling themselves comforting fables in which Republicans are the sole Bad Guys, and Democrats are always the Honorable Heroes, who never need to be held accountable. Without that accountability, Democratic politicians can rest easy knowing that they can issue press releases pledging to get tough on an issue like rail safety, but also knowing they may never have to actually deliver on those promises.",
