      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "One of those promises should be fixing the specific problem that the Obama administration created and that both the Trump and Biden administration refused to address — the problem of explosive hazmat trains somehow still not being classified as “high-hazard flammable trains” and therefore still not being subjected to tougher safety mandates.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
